## ============================================
## Tor Config — Dual SOCKS5 Proxy + Auto Rotate
## Arvind's setup — 2026-06-18
## ============================================

## === SOCKS5 PROXY PORTS ===
## Port 1: Translator Proxy 1
SocksPort 127.0.0.1:9050 IsolateDestAddr IsolateDestPort

## Port 2: Translator Proxy 2
SocksPort 127.0.0.1:9060 IsolateDestAddr IsolateDestPort

## === CONTROL PORT (for NEWNYM IP rotation) ===
ControlPort 9051
HashedControlPassword 16:REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_HASHED_PASSWORD

## === DNS THROUGH TOR (prevent leaks) ===
DNSPort 5353
AutomapHostsOnResolve 1

## === CIRCUIT SETTINGS ===
NewCircuitPeriod 600
MaxCircuitDirtiness 600

## === LOGGING ===
Log notice file /var/log/tor/notices.log
